Armando Trapaga

Professional Description

Name: Armando Gael Gonzalez Trapaga

Professional Profile

I am a dynamic and energetic professional with a unique ability to tackle challenges creatively and efficiently. With a vibrant and enthusiastic personality. I injects energy into every project i lead, motivating my team and creating a positive, collaborative work environment.

Despite my slightly chaotic nature, i excel in quickly adapting to change and unforeseen situations, finding innovative and effective solutions. My proactive approach and open mind allow me to address problems from different angles, ensuring successful outcomes.

Key Skills

  • Creativity and Innovation: Generates fresh and original ideas to solve complex problems.
  • Leadership: Motivates and guides his team with passion and determination.
  • Adaptability: Quickly adapts to new environments and challenges.
  • Effective Communication: Clearly and persuasively conveys ideas and concepts.
  • Time Management: Able to prioritize tasks and meet tight deadlines despite his unconventional approach.

Professional Experience

  • FreyreLab (2023 - Present)
    I am working as a co-author on the development of a tool specialized in the mass download of microarray data

Education

  • High School Diploma, Colegio Mentes de Oca
  • Currently Pursuing a Bachelors Degree in Genomic Sciences, National Autonomous University of Mexico (UNAM)
